@startuml
[*] --> CheckingStartup
CheckingStartup --> ReadyToUse : everything fine
ReadyToUse --> ReadyToUse : reset, activate, turn off
ReadyToUse --> ActivatedMonitoring : activated
ActivatedMonitoring --> Alarming : sensor triggered
Alarming --> Normal : password entered or time ends
Normal --> [*]
@enduml
